Project Plan
-create movies segments that can flow from one to another seamlessly
 (think video game sprites)
-motion capture (iPi soft) the movements to sell library to game companies
-motion capture (iPi soft) and create a 3d creature and use them for the videos
-user votes for effectiveness of moves
  have make sure one vote per user
-user favorites/ mastery achievements
-auto suggestions for next move
-develop a game where players can face each other using videos in the database
  build a character and develop skills.
-create a set of videos for the ibjff rules

